snippet: Scott Janssen, an Anchorage undertaker known as the Mushing Mortician, was flown to a hospital after a harrowing ordeal in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
abstract: American musher Scott Janssen is flown to a hospital after a harrowing crash in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
lead_paragraph: Scott Janssen, an Anchorage undertaker known as the Mushing Mortician, was flown to a hospital after a harrowing ordeal in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
